title: What does Zac, Ziggs, and Riven have in common
body:
They have a lot of bounce.
https://m.popkey.co/7e1062/jWxqe.gif

replies.body:
I say I cringe at these puns, but it's more of a "mfhhhhh". Kind of "nose exhale" if you will.

But anyway, +1.
I was about to cringe too, but then my mood bounced back.
SALTS- Smiled a little, then stopped
Bounce as in broken wings? Or am I making to much of a safe assumption.
Well her Broken wing does have a lot of bounce.
